-Thao-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-ohBo2IQtck_kzuPWG-Ebmw">Tái hạ - 塞下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Thao-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-tzEin01iG68zsm2nWGm0IQ">Tần Thao Ngọc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/T%E1%BA%A9u-b%C3%BAt-t%E1%BA%A1-M%E1%BA%A1nh-gi%C3%A1n-ngh%E1%BB%8B-k%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-tr%C3%A0/poem-cwd22cTED0FtlMGOAisk5w">Tẩu bút tạ Mạnh gián nghị ký tân trà - 走筆謝孟諫議寄新茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-u9rcZBkvQdaFAifcr_6CMA">Lư Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-sung-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%91c-qu%E1%BA%ADn-ph%C3%B2ng-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-MFF_HoVQ7OCaWWzHCcGVEw">Tống Vi thập lục bình sự sung Đồng Cốc quận phòng ngự phán quan - 送韋十六評事充同谷郡防禦判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Tr%C3%A0-giang-thu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-ca/poem-43N05C4Futansq7ZKSooaA">Trà giang thu nguyệt ca - 茶江秋月歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/T%C3%BAc-Ly-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-OoG8tEAyuKFpoVtEL7y3Eg">Túc Ly Phủ - 宿犛甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
